==================== 0.4 ====================
2010-01-08  Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>
	* *: Changed character-palette/characterpalette
		to charpick.
	* install.rdf: changed ID to charpick@ryanium.com.
	* chrome/content/charpick.xul, charpick.js:
		Copy directly after pushing the buttons.
	* chrome/content/about.xul, credits.xul:
		About dialog modified, and added credits dialog.
	* chrome/content/help.html, help.css:
		Moved help page to GitHub.
	* chrome/content/preferences.xul:
		Option for pasting with middle-clicks.
	* chrome/content/logo.png, logo-large.png:
		Logo updates.
	* chrome/locale: Locale updates.

==================== 0.3 ====================

2009-11-18  Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>

	* chrome/content/*: Fully customizable toolbar,
		with default palettes set to the GNOME one's.
	* chrome/content/style.css: Unicode characters
		can now display correctly.
	* chrome/content/help.*: Use a help page as
		a substitution of the previous dialog.

==================== 0.2.2 ====================

2009-11-03  Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>

	* chrome/content/style.css: Fixed the bug that menus
		are displayed in red when using themes.
		Thanks for Alan Martin who points out this bug.
	* install.rdf: Homepage URL also changed to the AMO one.
	* chrome/content/about.xul: Translator's name get listed
		in about dialog.

==================== 0.2.1 ====================

2009-10-08  Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>

	* chrome.manifest: Missing hu-HU declarating in chrome.manifest fixed.
		Thanks Mikes Kaszmán István for mentioning this.
	* chrome/locale/*: New locales for ru-RU and sr-RS.

==================== 0.2 ====================

2009-01-28  Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>

	* chrome/content/*: User interface improved,
		with a input field containing the characters
		you want and easy to copy.
	* chrome/locale/*: Locales for ca-AD, de-DE, hu-HU, nl-NL,
		pl-PL, pt-BR, tr-TR and uk-UA.
	* *: A brief introduction is added.
	* chrome/content/style.css: The bug that some characters
		were improperly displayed, esp. under GNOME, solved.

==================== 0.1.1 ====================

2008-07-16  Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>

	* chrome/locale/*/charpick.properties: Description localized.
	* chrome/locale/*: Locales for fr-FR, ja-JP, ko-KR, zh-CN.

==================== 0.1 ====================

2008-07-16  Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>
	* chrome/locale/character-palette.js: Fixed incompatibility with
		`textarea's.

==================== 0.0 ====================

